longBusinessSummary: H-Source Holdings Ltd., a technology company, operates in the healthcare industry. It offers a hospital-to-hospital transaction platform that provides a marketplace for members to buy, sell, and transfer excess inventory supplies and capital equipment with each other. The company's platform allows members to conduct transactions within integrated delivery networks and group purchasing organizations. H-Source Holdings Ltd. is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
